00:11:14.000 --> 00:11:20.000
 You take the user's email, you strip it, throw away any white space, you convert it to lowercase,

00:11:20.000 --> 00:11:29.000
 you encode it in UTF-8, and then you use the MD5, which is a hashing function, and make a hex digest.

00:11:29.000 --> 00:11:37.000
